title: DAZ3D - Lilja for Genesis 3 Female(s)
description:
Originally uploaded to KAT by IDKwhoToBe

--

"Original Link: 
http://www.daz3d.com/lilja-for-genesis-3-female-s




Details

Lilja is a beautiful girl for Genesis 3 Female. She comes with various eye, makeup and lip options. Both Iray and 3Delight materials are included.




What's Included and Features

Lilja (.DUF)
Character Preset
Shaping Presets
Full Shape Apply and Remove
Custom Head Shape Apply and Remove
Body Shape Apply and Remove
Material Options:
1 Character Base MAT w Nude Face
1 Anatomical Elements MAT
8 Makeup Options
8 Lip Colors
Natural Lips w gloss
6 Eye Colors
Normal Maps On/Off
Textures:
31 Texture, Bump and Specular Maps (4096 x 4096)
14 Texture, Bump and Transparency Maps (2048 x 2048)
This product uses the Genesis 3 Base Female UV Maps
Daz Studio 3Delight Material Presets (.DUF)
Daz Studio Iray Material Presets (.DUF)





I hope you all enjoy it!"
